<lb ed="T" n="0756c12"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0756c13" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 493</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0756c14" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead><note place="foot text" n="0756005" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0756005">佛說【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0756005"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>阿難四事經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="T" n="0756c15"/>
<lb n="0756c16" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">吳<note n="0756006" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">月支國居士＝代【宋】【元】，優婆塞【明】，月支優婆塞【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0756006">月支國居士【大】，代【宋】【元】，優婆塞【明】，月支優婆塞【宮】</note><app n="0756006"><lem wit="【大】">月支國居士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">代</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">優婆塞</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">月支優婆塞</rdg></app>支謙譯</byline>
<lb n="0756c17" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0756c1701">聞如是：</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0756c1704">一時，佛在拘夷那竭國，欲滅度。時阿
<lb n="0756c18" ed="T"/>難白佛言：「我念天龍、鬼神、帝<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0756007">王＝主【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0756007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王【大】＊，主【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0756007"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>、人民與佛
<lb ed="T" n="0756c19"/>相見，聞佛教誡，無不歡喜。在<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0756008">志＝心【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0756008">志【大】，心【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0756008"><lem wit="【大】">志</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>所願，或
<lb n="0756c20" ed="T"/>作沙門，得應真者；或有居家，奉行五戒，死
<lb ed="T" n="0756c21"/>得<note n="0756009" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">上＋（生）【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0756009">上【大】，上生【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0756009"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">上生</rdg></app>天者。<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0756010" place="foot text">今＝念【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0756010">今【大】，念【宮】</note><app n="0756010"><lem wit="【大】">今</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">念</rdg></app>佛去世，天龍、鬼神、帝王、人
<lb n="0756c22" ed="T"/>民及四輩弟子，當何恃賴得福得度？將當
<lb n="0756c23" ed="T"/>復從誰得之乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0756c2307" rend="inline">佛言：「善哉，善哉！阿難！慈心多
<lb n="0756c24" ed="T"/>愍。天人雜類，無不由汝得度脫者。吾去之後，
<lb n="0756c25" ed="T"/>世名五濁，人心憒憒，穢垢自亂，世多顛倒，
<lb n="0756c26" ed="T"/>賤善<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0756011" place="foot text">尊＝貴【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0756011">尊【大】，貴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0756011"><lem wit="【大】">尊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">貴</rdg></app>惡，此實可憂。世雖然者，吾有經籍、
<lb n="0756c27" ed="T"/>懇惻之戒，盡心遵行，福自歸身，汝莫憂也。吾
<lb n="0756c28" ed="T"/>雖去世，典籍續存，六度大法，不持之去，行
<lb n="0756c29" ed="T"/>者得度，非神授與。汝等不解吾之所言耶？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0756c2917">阿
<pb ed="T" xml:id="T14.0493.0757a" n="0757a"/>
<lb n="0757a01" ed="T"/>難即白：「願重說之。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0757a02"/><p xml:id="pT14p0757a0201">佛言：「大法有四，可從得福，亦可得道，<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0757001">（與得…當以）二十五字＝得福得道與侍（侍＝待【宋】）佛身正等難白佛為我解說四事佛言當【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757001a">與得佛身其福正等【大】，得福得道與待佛身正等【宋】，得福得道與侍佛身正等【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757001a"><lem wit="【大】">與得
<lb ed="T" n="0757a03"/>佛身、其福正等。」</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">得福得道與待佛身正等</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">得福得道與侍佛身正等</rdg></app></p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0757a0307"><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757001b">阿難又言願佛為我解釋四事【大】，難白佛為我解說四事【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757001b"><lem wit="【大】">阿難又言：「願佛為我解釋
<lb n="0757a04" ed="T"/>四事。」</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">難白佛為我解說四事</rdg></app></p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0757a0403"><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757001c">世尊曰當以【大】，佛言當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757001c"><lem wit="【大】">世尊曰：「當以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛言當</rdg></app>慈心育養幼弱，見禽獸、蟲
<lb n="0757a05" ed="T"/>蛾下賤仰人活者，常當愍念，隨其所食，令
<lb ed="T" n="0757a06"/>得穌息，莫得加刀杖傷絕其命，惻愴慈心，當
<lb n="0757a07" ed="T"/>如慈母。天龍、鬼神、帝<app corresp="#0756007" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>、人民，有行此慈者，
<lb ed="T" n="0757a08"/>其得大福，與侍佛身功德正等。此謂一事
<lb n="0757a09" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" n="0757002" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔也〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757002">也【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0757002"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0757a0902" rend="inline">「世有災異，水旱不調，五穀不豐，人民飢
<lb n="0757a10" ed="T"/>饉，不安本土，志欲叛亡；王及臣民，富有倉
<lb n="0757a11" ed="T"/>穀，當惟無常，身命難保，<note place="foot text" n="0757003" resp="Taisho" type="orig">勿＝愚【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757003">勿【大】，愚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757003"><lem wit="【大】">勿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">愚</rdg></app>愛<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757004" place="foot text">寶＋（重）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757004">寶【大】，寶重【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757004"><lem wit="【大】">寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">寶重</rdg></app>穀，知愛
<lb ed="T" n="0757a12"/>人命，當起悲心，出穀廩假，<note n="0757005" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">賙＝周【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賙【大】，周【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757005"><lem wit="【大】">賙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">周</rdg></app>諸窮乏，以濟
<lb ed="T" n="0757a13"/>其命，安居本土。若意慳貪，不欲布施，當諦
<lb n="0757a14" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757006" place="foot text">計＝忖【三】</note><note n="0757006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">計【大】，忖【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757006"><lem wit="【大】">計</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">忖</rdg></app>念：『人初來生，魂神空來，依因<note place="foot text" n="0757007" type="orig" resp="Taisho">二＝姻【三】，恩【宮】</note><note n="0757007" type="mod" resp="CBETA">二【大】，姻【宋】【元】【明】，恩【宮】</note><app n="0757007"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">姻</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">恩</rdg></app>親情
<lb n="0757a15" ed="T"/>欲之氣，以成己體。在母腹中，十月乃生，得
<lb ed="T" n="0757a16"/>親喜悅，可得全命。愁忿之<note place="foot text" n="0757008" resp="Taisho" type="orig">日＝曰【宋】【元】</note><note n="0757008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日【大】，曰【宋】【元】</note><app n="0757008"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>，即<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757009" place="foot text">切＝剋【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757009">切【大】，剋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757009"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">剋</rdg></app>絕之，
<lb ed="T" n="0757a17"/><note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757010" place="foot text">困＝因【三】</note><note n="0757010" type="mod" resp="CBETA">困【大】，因【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757010"><lem wit="【大】">困</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">因</rdg></app>極乃終，魂神不滅，復更求身。豪貴貧賤，
<lb n="0757a18" ed="T"/>皆由宿行。官爵俸祿、國土珍寶，無為迷惑，以
<lb n="0757a19" ed="T"/>亂高德，至其壽終，身及珍寶，故留世間，不
<lb n="0757a20" ed="T"/>隨己去。常當慈心，練<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757011" place="foot text">行＝存【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757011">行【大】，存【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757011"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">存</rdg></app>經道，以佛明<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757012" place="foot text">教＝法【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757012">教【大】，法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757012"><lem wit="【大】">教</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>，觀
<lb ed="T" n="0757a21"/>視人物，如幻如化，如夢如響，一切皆空，不
<lb ed="T" n="0757a22"/>可久保，觀世皆爾，此為真諦。世人愚惑，心
<lb ed="T" n="0757a23"/>存顛倒，自欺自誤，猶以金價，買<note place="foot text" n="0757013" resp="Taisho" type="orig">鍮＝塗【宮】</note><note n="0757013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鍮【大】，塗【宮】</note><app n="0757013"><lem wit="【大】">鍮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">塗</rdg></app>銅也，身
<lb ed="T" n="0757a24"/>死神去，當墮三塗。』諦思如此；急當布施，與
<lb ed="T" n="0757a25"/>身命競，貧窮乞匃、羸老疾病，隨所當<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0757014">與＝得【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757014">與【大】，得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757014"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>，
<lb ed="T" n="0757a26"/>莫令<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757015" place="foot text">命＝死【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757015">命【大】，死【宮】</note><app n="0757015"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">死</rdg></app>絕。執心如此，十方諸佛、開士大人、
<lb ed="T" n="0757a27"/>天龍鬼神，無不愍之。至於壽終，魂神所生，
<lb ed="T" n="0757a28"/>輒受豪貴，身意俱安，災害不生，具獲上願，
<lb ed="T" n="0757a29"/>如佛在時，供養佛身，正等無異。此謂二事
<pb ed="T" n="0757b" xml:id="T14.0493.0757b"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0757b01"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757016" place="foot text">也＝世【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757016">也【大】，世【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757016"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">世</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0757b0102" rend="inline">「<note place="foot text" n="0757017" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔國中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757017">國中【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757017"><lem wit="【大】">國中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>多有盜賊水火，災異變生，毒氣
<lb ed="T" n="0757b02"/><note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0757018">〔流布〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757018" type="mod" resp="CBETA">流布【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757018"><lem wit="【大】">流布</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，疾病縱橫，悉是海中龍神鬼王之所為
<lb ed="T" n="0757b03"/><app type="star" corresp="#0757002"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，故得此<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757019" place="foot text">毒＋（氣）【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757019">毒【大】，毒氣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757019"><lem wit="【大】">毒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">毒氣</rdg></app>，重病憂惱。此諸鬼神龍者，皆
<lb n="0757b04" ed="T"/>是世人所為射獵、屠殺、<note n="0757b0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">漁【CB】【麗-CB】，魚【大】</note><app n="0757b0401"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">漁<note type="cf1">K20n0817_p1127c10</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">魚</rdg></app>網中毒死者。其魂
<lb ed="T" n="0757b05"/>神或<note n="0757020" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">墮海中為龍＝海中【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757020">墮海中為龍【大】，海中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757020"><lem wit="【大】">墮海中為龍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">海中</rdg></app>，或為有力<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0757021">太＝大【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">太【大】，大【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757021"><lem wit="【大】">太</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">大</rdg></app>神化生之
<lb ed="T" n="0757b06"/>類，皆知宿命，忿怒宿怨，<note n="0757022" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">因＝故【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">因【大】，故【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757022"><lem wit="【大】">因</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">故</rdg></app>作霧露，吐<note place="foot text" n="0757023" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔惡〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757023">惡【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757023"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>毒
<lb n="0757b07" ed="T"/>氣，雨其國<note place="foot text" n="0757024" type="orig" resp="Taisho">中＝土【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757024">中【大】，土【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757024"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">土</rdg></app>。其時人民，或中毒死者，或但
<lb ed="T" n="0757b08"/>得病者，有相塗<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0757025">〔污〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">污【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757025"><lem wit="【大】">污</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>者，<note place="foot text" n="0757026" resp="Taisho" type="orig">皆由＝此皆【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆由【大】，此皆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757026"><lem wit="【大】">皆由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此皆</rdg></app>世人所作不仁，
<lb n="0757b09" ed="T"/>殘殺物命，展轉相怨。<note place="foot text" n="0757027" type="orig" resp="Taisho">手自＝自手【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757027" type="mod" resp="CBETA">手自【大】，自手【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757027"><lem wit="【大】">手自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">自手</rdg></app>殺者，中毒即死；
<lb n="0757b10" ed="T"/>助其喜者，皆更困病；或相塗污、<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757028" place="foot text">〔不相塗污〕－【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757028">不相塗污【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0757028"><lem wit="【大】">不相塗污</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0757b11" ed="T"/>者，皆由食肉有相分者、不相分者。<note n="0757029" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">聽聰＝聰明【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757029" type="mod" resp="CBETA">聽聰【大】，聰明【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757029"><lem wit="【大】">聽聰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聰明</rdg></app>之
<lb ed="T" n="0757b12"/>士，覺知殺罪<note n="0757030" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">追＝遺【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757030">追【大】，遺【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757030"><lem wit="【大】">追</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遺</rdg></app>人不置，以己度彼，正等無
<lb ed="T" n="0757b13"/>異。如此奉行，佛之弘道，行四等心——慈、悲、喜、
<lb ed="T" n="0757b14"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757031" place="foot text">護＝捨【三】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757031">護【大】，捨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757031"><lem wit="【大】">護</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">捨</rdg></app>——福自歸身。若彼殺<note n="0757032" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">家＝害【宮】</note><note n="0757032" type="mod" resp="CBETA">家【大】，害【宮】</note><app n="0757032"><lem wit="【大】">家</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">害</rdg></app>，以肉與己，慎莫
<lb ed="T" n="0757b15"/>食之。不食<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0757033">之＝肉【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757033">之【大】，肉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757033"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">肉</rdg></app>者，雖處惡世、盜賊災變、毒氣
<lb ed="T" n="0757b16"/>之時，雖處其中，不相塗染。其帝<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0757034">王＝主【明】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757034">王【大】＊，主【明】＊</note><app n="0757034"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">主</rdg></app>、人民<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757035" place="foot text">富＝當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">富【大】，當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757035"><lem wit="【大】">富</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當</rdg></app>
<lb n="0757b17" ed="T"/>有盈穀，孤獨鰥寡，衣食不充，疾病困<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757036" place="foot text">篤＝苦【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757036">篤【大】，苦【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757036"><lem wit="【大】">篤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">苦</rdg></app>，無
<lb ed="T" n="0757b18"/>以自濟，當給醫藥、糜粥消息，令其得愈，命
<lb n="0757b19" ed="T"/>不橫盡。當明此人宿命行惡，不信三尊，背真
<lb ed="T" n="0757b20"/>向偽，慳貪所致，罪福分明，慎莫為惡；亦當
<lb ed="T" n="0757b21"/>慈心，以佛經法，教訓愚癡，令持經道。若<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757037" place="foot text">活＝治【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">活【大】，治【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757037"><lem wit="【大】">活</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">治</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0757b22"/>一人，使病得愈，示之善道，<note place="foot text" n="0757038" type="orig" resp="Taisho">令＝今【明】</note><note n="0757038" type="mod" resp="CBETA">令【大】，今【明】</note><app n="0757038"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">今</rdg></app>持五戒，終身
<lb ed="T" n="0757b23"/>清潔，與侍佛身，其福正等。是謂三事<app type="star" corresp="#0757002"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0757b24"/><p xml:id="pT14p0757b2401">「世有高節，清潔無欲，沙門梵志，懷抱經典，
<lb ed="T" n="0757b25"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757039" place="foot text">言輒＝輒言【三】</note><note n="0757039" type="mod" resp="CBETA">言輒【大】，輒言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757039"><lem wit="【大】">言輒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">輒言</rdg></app>法律。帝<app corresp="#0757034" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757040" place="foot text">臣＝人【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0757040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臣【大】＊，人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0757040"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>民，心當恭肅，詣<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757041" place="foot text">稟＝彼【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757041" type="mod" resp="CBETA">稟【大】，彼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757041"><lem wit="【大】">稟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">彼</rdg></app>律
<lb ed="T" n="0757b26"/>行。此曹高士口之所陳，皆是諸佛<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0757042">之遺典也＝說之遺典【三】，之遺典【宮】</note><note n="0757042" type="mod" resp="CBETA">之遺典也【大】，說之遺典【宋】【元】【明】，之遺典【宮】</note><app n="0757042"><lem wit="【大】">之遺典
<lb n="0757b27" ed="T"/>也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">說之遺典</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">之遺典</rdg></app>，令人去惡就善，恩倍於親百有餘分，使
<lb ed="T" n="0757b28"/>人壽終不墮三塗，常當慈心恭肅向之。寧<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0757043">洋＝烊【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757043">洋【大】，烊【宮】</note><app n="0757043"><lem wit="【大】">洋</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">烊</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0757b29"/>銅灌口，利刀截舌，慎莫謗毀此清潔之人；
<pb ed="T" n="0757c" xml:id="T14.0493.0757c"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0757c01"/>寧<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0757044">自斷手＝就斷首【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757044" type="mod" resp="CBETA">自斷手【大】，就斷首【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757044"><lem wit="【大】">自斷手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">就斷首</rdg></app>，莫加之痛；寧自<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text" n="0757045">剖＝割【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757045">剖【大】，割【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757045"><lem wit="【大】">剖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">割</rdg></app>腹，出心燒
<lb n="0757c02" ed="T"/>之，無怒此人。設使愚者見佛經道，明知去就，
<lb ed="T" n="0757c03"/>由遠頑闇之<note n="0757046" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">群＋（邪）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757046">群【大】，群邪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757046"><lem wit="【大】">群</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">群邪</rdg></app>，馳就賢者之眾，講受聖典
<lb n="0757c04" ed="T"/>以成高德。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0757c0405" rend="inline">「沙門梵志，無以貿買求利為身穢
<lb ed="T" n="0757c05"/>垢，心清行淨，猶明月珠；<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757047" place="foot text">護＝故【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757047">護【大】，故【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757047"><lem wit="【大】">護</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">故</rdg></app>持應器，勞身乞
<lb n="0757c06" ed="T"/>食，供口即止，不畜遺餘；或居寺舍，或處山澤、
<lb ed="T" n="0757c07"/>樹下、塚間，皆知宿命；分別真偽制作經籍，為
<lb ed="T" n="0757c08"/>世橋梁，慈心多愍；坐起咒願帝<app corresp="#0757034" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>、<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0757048" place="foot text">臣＝人【明】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757048">臣【大】，人【明】</note><app n="0757048"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">人</rdg></app>民，令
<lb n="0757c09" ed="T"/>國平夷。如此高士，德訓諸天、龍、鬼惻心，不
<lb n="0757c10" ed="T"/><note n="0757049" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">務＝豫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757049" type="mod" resp="CBETA">務【大】，豫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757049"><lem wit="【大】">務</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">豫</rdg></app>世俗故，不為情欲之失，所見歎述耳。國王
<lb ed="T" n="0757c11"/><app type="star" corresp="#0757040"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>民，若有<note n="0757050" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757050">智【大】，知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757050"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>者，當尋求之，供所當得衣食
<lb n="0757c12" ed="T"/>床臥<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757051" place="foot text">疾病＝病瘐【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0757051">疾病【大】，病瘐【宮】</note><app n="0757051"><lem wit="【大】">疾病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">病瘐</rdg></app>醫藥，使其安隱，得<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757052" place="foot text">講＝讚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757052" type="mod" resp="CBETA">講【大】，讚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757052"><lem wit="【大】">講</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">讚</rdg></app>經戒，敷演
<lb ed="T" n="0757c13"/>訓導，坐禪念定，或從得道，或死得上天；衣食
<lb n="0757c14" ed="T"/>一國穢濁之人，不如盡心供養清淨道士一
<lb ed="T" n="0757c15"/>人，其福弘大，如佛在時，供養佛身正等無異。
<lb n="0757c16" ed="T"/>此<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0757053" place="foot text">謂＝諸【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0757053">謂【大】，諸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757053"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">諸</rdg></app>四事<app type="star" corresp="#0757002"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0757c1606">「帝<app type="star" corresp="#0757034"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app><app corresp="#0757040" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人</rdg></app>民，<note n="0757054" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">視＝親【三】</note><note n="0757054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">視【大】，親【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757054"><lem wit="【大】">視</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">親</rdg></app>此輩人，天
<lb ed="T" n="0757c17"/>龍、鬼神，無不擁護助之歡喜<note n="0757055" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔者也〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者也【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757055"><lem wit="【大】">者也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。」</p>
<lb n="0757c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0757c1801">佛告阿難：「吾前世時，行此四事，展轉受福，
<lb ed="T" n="0757c19"/>自致得佛。吾以是故，重說四事。阿難！汝當
<lb ed="T" n="0757c20"/><note n="0757056" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔廣〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0757056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">廣【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0757056"><lem wit="【大】">廣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>為諸天、帝<app type="star" corresp="#0757034"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">主</rdg></app>、<app corresp="#0757040" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人</rdg></app>民說之，所作善行，自
<lb ed="T" n="0757c21"/>得其福，終不唐捐。吾將滅度，四事<note n="0757057" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">（屬）＋累【三】</note><note n="0757057" type="mod" resp="CBETA">累【大】，屬累【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0757057"><lem wit="【大】">累</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">屬累</rdg></app>汝。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0757c2116" rend="inline">阿
<lb n="0757c22" ed="T"/>難聞經，且悲且喜，前以頭面，為佛作禮。</p></cb:div>
